subject: Re:  Hello
body:
Hello Carol B. Tom, 

It's a pleasure to meet you! As the UPS Chief Executive Officer, I'm sure you have a lot of interesting insights and experiences. Could you share some of your day-to-day responsibilities in this role?

Best wishes,
Michael

body:
Hello Carol B. Tom,

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Michael
